OL,3,CCouncillors removed from committee
OL,4,Cafter 'badly behaved' SEND kids
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FThree councillors at Warwickshire
OL,8,FCounty Council about children with
OL,9,Fspecial educational needs have been
OL,10,Fremoved from their committee.
OL,12,FThe comments during a debate on SEND
OL,13,Fprovision in the county questioned
OL,14,Fwhether some children "were just
OL,15,Freally badly behaved", and "needed a
OL,16,Fform of strict correction".
