OL,3,CCouncillors removed from committee
OL,4,Cafter 'badly behaved' SEND kids
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FCllr Jeff Morgan, Cllr Brian
OL,8,FHammersley and Cllr Clare Golby, all
OL,9,FConservatives, have subsequently been
OL,10,Fcriticised for the language they used
OL,11,Fon 25 January.
OL,13,FCllr Morgan, the former cabinet member
OL,14,Ffor children and young people queried
OL,15,Fwhether some "were just really badly
OL,16,Fbehaved" and "needed a form of strict
OL,17,Fcorrection."
OL,19,FCllr Hammersley asked: "Was there
OL,20,Fsomething in the water?" and "Where
OL,21,Fwere they all when I was at school?"
