OL,3,CCouncillors removed from committee
OL,4,Cafter 'badly behaved' SEND kids
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FCllr Clare Golby questioned: "What
OL,8,Fcomes down to parenting and what comes
OL,9,Fdown to SEND issues ` how do we
OL,10,Fidentify that and what pathways do we
OL,11,Fput people on that perhaps don't have
OL,12,Fan SEND need but do have parenting
OL,13,Fskill shortages?"
OL,15,FIn a statement Warwickshire County
OL,16,FCouncil said, "Whilst a formal
OL,17,Finvestigation is underway, it can be
OL,18,Fconfirmed the councillors concerned
OL,19,Fhave been removed from the Overview
OL,20,Fand Scrutiny Committee. Replacements
OL,21,Fwill be appointed in due course."
